attributes.value: Horus, The God of The Sky

metadata.name: Meet The Maker #1
metadata.description: Meet the Maker is the fourth collection from Bored Mummy Waking Up, and is a collection of 3,888 collectibles in the form of Ancient Egyptian Deities. Each and every one of them have been hand drawn carefully and made pristine with impeccable details by our talented artists. There are a total of 7 attributes and over 120 traits!
